Went this afternoon with family.
Place is still new and they still seem to be figuring out the operational stuff in the meanwhile expect quite a bit of chaos,  possibly spoilt food and confusing service  We ordered Paav bhaaji, sev puri and paani puri.
Paav bhaaji was ok and paani puri potatoes were spoilt.
Ok, have to leave now.
The fire alarm just went off accidentally and chaos rules.
In the meanwhile i get 10% off as an apology for the rotten potatoes in the paani puri.
Doubt this place will be around in 6 months and will not miss it either.

